Oh man! Only 4 more days and I get to be home for a month.
It's gonna rock, although I will miss lots of people here though.
Hmm...too much shit to do for finals. No sir, I dont like it.
I think there will be some fun to be had before we all leave this week...oh yeah!
Keep on rockin'.
Um...yah, thats it. 
Bye.

I need home. College is high school. theres really no difference. People are still immature and shallow.
On a lighter note, skinny, twitchy greg chased kev and pete around the entire dorm cause they called him gay. It was awesome. And I made cards for old people in homes. Im so nice.
When I get home there will be band recording, and although we are far from good, it will be fun.
I need home.
*Katharine, you rock...psych!!*

Oh man, today was so mostly boring.  Then we got the idea to go to Applebee's and waste two hours...and kill $90.  Definately good.  Ah, some good times with the Purchase kids.  Cant wait to be home in 15 days though.  It will be good.  
Im still pissed about the damn Christmas board.  The RC is making US put up a new one.  Bitch!
How bout some 'fuck you' for her?
                                               FUCK YOU!!!!

Its almost 2 in the morning. Im not tired. Im bored out of my mind. Still not in a good mood. I want to go home, its more fun being pissed there. Im sick of everyone. I dont like being around everyone all the time. Im antisocial. Theres nothing to do. Im writing in this thing again. It doesnt seem to click for some people that this is just a joke. Thats why it makes no sense. How can you write your feelings in here? How can you complain in this? Is it this thing thats making me mad? Oh well, Fuck you anyway.  Fuck is an amazing word. Where would we be without it? Nowhere! 
Vinny and Greg the Jew are fighting in the hall.  Gregs gonna get put in an oven.

The campus is flooded so I went swimming, then the sun came up and it got windy like a tornado, so I went flying.  Im watching Ed, Edd and Eddy.  Its fun.  Im bored.  OH, and they took down our fucking Christmas board!  We drew on it and the RC thought it was too graphic and disturbing and disgusting so she took it down.  So I crapped in front of her door and lit it on fire.

Oh man, its been so long since Ive written in this thing. Im having withdrawl. Im just sitting in my room with Kevin, Ryan, and Peter watching Requiem for a Dream.  Crazy fuckin movie, lemme tell you...the story of my life.  Killer fridges and shit.  So yeah, I think after the movie I'll go scope out who's still awake on the floor and then maybe go to bed.  Its Atiya's birthday..yesterday? today? I dont remember, but happy birthday!!  So after I sleep, Im going to wake up and not do anything because its my day off. I'd give you a blow by blow of what Im going to do, but that would be copying Claire.  And I'd just complain all the time in here, but that would be just like....everyone on this site.  Id rather discuss shit with a real person than talking to kids on a computer.  PETER DRAWS CARTOONS GOOD!!
    Hey....fuck you!!

Can you believe this? A live Journal....Me?  Yeah, dont worry, it wont be serious. Most of the time Ill make fun of you little kids. Ill talk about how sad I always am, and all the things that happen to me everyday.  And Ill write down ALL my problems here, but I wont tell you what they are because its so much fun that way.  Isnt that the point of Live Journal?  If you disagree, it might be your opinion, but you'll be wrong.  So, welcome to LJ to me, and fuck the rest of you.
